<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ca">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BET3d5 – Apostes de Castells</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--green:#00d04b;--green-dark:#00a038;--bg:#0d1117;--bg2:#161b22;--bg3:#1f2937;--bg4:#252d3a;--border:#2a3441;--text:#e6edf3;--text-dim:#8b949e;--text-muted:#4a5568;--gold:#f0b400;--red:#f85149;--accent:#1a8cff}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh}
header{background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:2px solid var(--green);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 24px;height:58px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.2rem;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--green);text-shadow:0 0 20px #00d04b55}
.logo em{color:var(--text);font-style:normal;font-size:1rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;margin-left:8px;vertical-align:middle}
.btn{cursor:pointer;border:none;border-radius:4px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.5px;padding:8px 18px;transition:all .15s}
.btn-green{background:var(--green);color:#000}.btn-green:hover{background:var(--green-dark)}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-dim)}.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green)}
.btn-red{background:var(--red);color:#fff}.btn-red:hover{background:#c73040}
nav{background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;padding:0 24px;overflow-x:auto}
nav button{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-dim);font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.5px;padding:10px 18px;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}
nav button.active{color:var(--green);border-bottom-color:var(--green)}nav button:hover{color:var(--text)}
.ticker{background:var(--bg3);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center}
.ticker-inner{display:flex;gap:48px;animation:tick 35s linear infinite;white-space:nowrap;padding-left:100%}
.ticker-item{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim)}.ticker-item b{color:var(--green)}
@keyframes tick{from{transform:translateX(0)}to{transform:translateX(-200%)}}
.main-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 310px;min-height:calc(100vh - 120px)}
.left-panel{padding:16px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);overflow-y:auto}
.right-panel{padding:16px;background:var(--bg2);position:sticky;top:120px;height:calc(100vh - 120px);overflow-y:auto}
@media(max-width:768px){.main-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}.right-panel{position:static;height:auto}}
.sec-title{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);padding:4px 0 10px}
.diada-card{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:10px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.diada-card:hover{border-color:var(--green)}.diada-card.active{border-color:var(--green);background:var(--bg4)}
.diada-title{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem}
.diada-meta{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:3px}
.diada-colles{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px}
.tag{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 7px;font-size:.72rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:var(--green)}
.colla-block{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;overflow:hidden}
.colla-head{background:var(--bg4);padding:10px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px}
.colla-head-name{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem}
.colla-head-meta{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.lvl-badge{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 8px}
.gent-badge{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--accent);background:rgba(26,140,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(26,140,255,.3);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 8px}
.slot-block{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.slot-block:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.slot-head{background:var(--bg3);padding:6px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.slot-lbl{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;min-width:80px}
.slot-lbl.castell{color:var(--accent)}.slot-lbl.pilar{color:var(--gold)}
.slot-chosen{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text-dim);background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:1px 8px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif}
.cat-bar{padding:3px 14px;background:var(--bg4)}
.cat-lbl{font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase}
.mrow{display:flex;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .1s}
.mrow:hover{background:var(--bg3)}.mrow.sel{background:#00d04b0d}
.mrow-name{flex:1;padding:7px 14px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.92rem}
.mrow-sub{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-dim);font-weight:400;display:block}
.mrow-btn{cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);padding:5px 14px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;margin:5px 10px;min-width:62px;text-align:center;transition:all .15s}
.mrow-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:#1a8cff11}
.mrow-btn.sel{background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);color:#000}
.mrow-btn .ql{display:block;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:400;opacity:.7}
.bs-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--green);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
.bs-count{background:var(--green);color:#000;border-radius:12px;font-size:.72rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;padding:2px 10px}
.bet-item{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;margin-bottom:7px;position:relative}
.bet-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start}
.bet-colla{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--green)}
.bet-castle{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;margin-top:2px}
.bet-type{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:2px}
.bet-odd{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--gold);line-height:1}
.rm{cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1rem;position:absolute;top:7px;right:9px;transition:color .1s;line-height:1}
.rm:hover{color:var(--red)}
.bs-total{background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:12px;margin-top:10px}
.bs-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:5px}
.bs-main{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:8px;margin-top:6px}
.val{color:var(--gold)}
.stake-wrap{margin-top:10px}
.stake-lbl{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:4px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.stake-inp{width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;color:var(--text);padding:8px 12px;font-size:1rem;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;outline:none;transition:border-color .15s}
.stake-inp:focus{border-color:var(--green)}
.empty-bs{text-align:center;padding:36px 0;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.85rem}
.empty-bs .ico{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px}
.overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:#000c;z-index:1000;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;overflow-y:auto;padding:20px 0}
.overlay.open{display:flex}
.modal{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:26px;width:90%;max-width:700px;margin:auto}
.modal-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.7rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:11px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
.close-btn{cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem}.close-btn:hover{color:var(--text)}
.tabs{display:flex;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:18px}
.tab{cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;color:var(--text-dim);font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.88rem;letter-spacing:.5px;padding:8px 16px;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:all .15s}
.tab.active{color:var(--green);border-bottom-color:var(--green)}
.tc{display:none}.tc.active{display:block}
.flabel{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-dim);display:block;margin-bottom:5px;margin-top:14px}
.finput,.fselect{width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;color:var(--text);padding:9px 12px;font-size:.93rem;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;outline:none;transition:border-color .15s}
.finput:focus,.fselect:focus{border-color:var(--green)}.fselect option{background:var(--bg2)}
.colles-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;margin-top:6px}
.chk-lbl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:7px 11px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-size:.88rem}
.chk-lbl:hover{border-color:var(--green)}.chk-lbl input{accent-color:var(--green);width:15px;height:15px;cursor:pointer}
.lvl-row{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:12px;margin-bottom:6px}
.lvl-row-name{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--text)}
.lvl-row-fields{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.lvl-row-field label{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-dim);display:block;margin-bottom:4px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.lvl-sel{width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;color:var(--text);padding:7px 8px;font-size:.85rem;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.lvl-sel:focus{border-color:var(--green)}
.info-box{background:var(--bg3);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:4px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:10px}
.dl-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:11px 13px;margin-bottom:7px}
.dl-item .acts{display:flex;gap:7px;margin-left:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.no-content{text-align:center;padding:48px 0;color:var(--text-muted)}.no-content .big{font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:8px}
.separator{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:14px 0}
.hint{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:7px 12px;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:12px}
.hint b{color:var(--text)}
.c-d3{color:#888}.c-d4{color:#aaa}.c-d5{color:#4a9eff}.c-d6{color:#00d04b}.c-d7{color:#f0b400}.c-d8{color:#f85149}.c-d9{color:#ff44ff}
.bd-d3{border-left:2px solid #88888822}.bd-d4{border-left:2px solid #aaaaaa22}.bd-d5{border-left:2px solid #4a9eff33}.bd-d6{border-left:2px solid #00d04b33}.bd-d7{border-left:2px solid #f0b40033}.bd-d8{border-left:2px solid #f8514933}.bd-d9{border-left:2px solid #ff44ff33}
.fade{animation:fadeIn .2s ease}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.fb-status{font-size:.72rem;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.5px}
.fb-ok{background:rgba(0,208,75,.12);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(0,208,75,.3)}
.fb-err{background:rgba(248,81,73,.12);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.3)}
.loading{text-align:center;padding:40px;color:var(--text-muted)}
.spinner{width:32px;height:32px;border:3px solid var(--border);border-top-color:var(--green);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .7s linear infinite;margin:0 auto 12px}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:2000;background:var(--bg4);border:1px solid var(--green);border-radius:6px;padding:12px 18px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--text);transform:translateY(80px);opacity:0;transition:all .3s;pointer-events:none;max-width:340px}
.toast.show{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}
.edit-colla-row{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;margin-bottom:6px}
.edit-colla-name{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.edit-colla-fields{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px}
.edit-colla-field label{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-dim);display:block;margin-bottom:3px;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.edit-colla-field select{width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;color:var(--text);padding:6px 8px;font-size:.83rem;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.edit-colla-field select:focus{border-color:var(--green)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<header>
  <div class="logo">BET<span style="color:var(--text)">3</span>d5<em>Apostes de Castells</em></div>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px">
    <span class="fb-status fb-err" id="fb-status">● Connectant...</span>
    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="openAdmin()">⚙ ADMIN</button>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="ticker">
  <div class="ticker-inner" id="ticker-inner">
    <span class="ticker-item">Carregant quotes...</span>
  </div>
</div>

<nav>
  <button class="active" onclick="showSec('apostes',this)">🏆 Apostes</button>
  <button onclick="showSec('comunitat',this)">👥 Apostes de la gent</button>
  <button onclick="showSec('colles',this)">🏴 Colles</button>
</nav>

<div id="sec-apostes">
  <div class="main-layout">
    <div class="left-panel">
      <div class="sec-title">Diades disponibles</div>
      <div id="diades-list"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div>Carregant diades...</div></div>
      <div id="betting-area" style="display:none">
        <div class="separator"></div>
        <div class="sec-title">Mercat d'apostes</div>
        <div class="hint">Per cada colla pots apostar fins a <b>3 castells</b> (1r, 2n, 3r) i <b>1 pilar</b>. Cada aposta és "X <b>o superior</b>". La gent prevista es configura per colla.</div>
        <div id="markets"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-panel">
      <div class="bs-title">Butxaca <span class="bs-count" id="bs-count">0</span></div>
      <div id="bs-body">
        <div class="empty-bs"><div class="ico">🎪</div>Selecciona apostes del mercat</div>
      </div>
      <div id="bs-footer" style="display:none">
        <div class="bs-total">
          <div class="bs-row"><span>Quota combinada</span><span id="tot-odd" style="color:var(--gold);font-family:'Bebas Neue';font-size:1.1rem">1.00</span></div>
          <div class="stake-wrap">
            <div class="stake-lbl">Nom / Àlies</div>
            <input class="stake-inp" type="text" id="bettor-name" placeholder="El teu nom o àlies" maxlength="30" style="margin-bottom:8px">
            <div class="stake-lbl">Import (€)</div>
            <input class="stake-inp" type="number" id="stake" value="10" min="1" max="9999" oninput="calcBs()">
          </div>
          <div class="bs-main"><span>Guany potencial</span><span class="val" id="pot-win">10.00 €</span></div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-green" style="width:100%;margin-top:10px;padding:12px;font-size:1rem" onclick="placeBet()">APOSTAR ARA</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="sec-colles" style="display:none">
  <div style="padding:20px;max-width:900px">
    <div class="sec-title">Informació de colles</div>
    <div id="colles-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:10px"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="sec-comunitat" style="display:none">
  <div style="padding:20px;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="sec-title">Apostes de la comunitat</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center">
      <select class="fselect" id="filter-diada" onchange="renderComunitat()" style="max-width:260px;padding:7px 10px;font-size:.85rem">
        <option value="">Totes les diades</option>
      </select>
      <span id="comunitat-count" style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-muted)"></span>
    </div>
    <div id="comunitat-list">
      <div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div>Carregant apostes...</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ADMIN MODAL -->
<div class="overlay" id="admin-overlay">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-title">⚙ Administració <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeAdmin()">✕</button></div>
    <div class="tabs">
      <button class="tab active" onclick="aTab('nova',this)">Nova Diada</button>
      <button class="tab" onclick="aTab('gestio',this)">Gestió</button>
      <button class="tab" onclick="aTab('params',this)">Paràmetres</button>
    </div>

    <div class="tc active" id="tc-nova">
      <label class="flabel">Nom de la Diada</label>
      <input class="finput" id="d-name" placeholder="Ex: Diada de Sant Jordi 2025">
      <label class="flabel">Data</label>
      <input class="finput" id="d-date" type="date">
      <label class="flabel">Colles participants</label>
      <div class="colles-grid" id="colla-checks"></div>
      <div id="lvl-section" style="display:none">
        <label class="flabel" style="margin-top:18px">Configuració per colla</label>
        <div class="info-box" style="margin-bottom:12px">
          💡 <b>Nivell</b>: com va la colla en aquesta diada (afecta les quotes).<br>
          👥 <b>Gent prevista</b>: assistència esperada per a la actuació d'aquesta colla concreta.
        </div>
        <div id="lvl-selectors"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-green" style="margin-top:18px;padding:10px 28px" onclick="crearDiada()">CREAR DIADA</button>
    </div>

    <div class="tc" id="tc-gestio"><div id="gestio-list"></div></div>

    <div class="tc" id="tc-params">
      <div class="info-box">Quota = <b>(1 / prob_ajustada) × modificador × (1 − marge)</b>.<br>Nivell alt → prob més alta → quotes més baixes. Gent alta → més pressió → quotes lleugerament més altes.</div>
      <label class="flabel">Modificador global (1.0 = neutre)</label>
      <input class="finput" type="number" id="g-mod" value="1.0" step="0.05" min="0.5" max="2.0" oninput="previewParams()">
      <label class="flabel">Marge de la casa (%)</label>
      <input class="finput" type="number" id="g-margin" value="8" step="1" min="0" max="25" oninput="previewParams()">
      <div class="info-box" id="param-preview" style="margin-top:10px"></div>
      <button class="btn 